{"tid":2036624,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ViuTV]歎息橋 一至五 2130-2230 (20)","createTime":"2020-05-26T14:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T14:25:12.000Z","uid":111555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"32ac8a07b268f0a69e7124ee3681072306dde547","tid":2036624,"uid":111555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OzU5jhM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOzU5jhM.jpg&h=ac3b4706&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pewDsiz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpewDsiz.jpg&h=4a60e8fa&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">《歎息橋》(The Gutter)</div><br />\n<br />\n《歎息橋》嘅英文名 The Gutter，其實係引自王爾德嘅名句：<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><em>「我們都活在陰溝裡，但有些人仍然仰望星空。」<br />\n（We are all in the gutter, but some of us are looking at the stars.）</em></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong>編劇</strong> 黃綺琳<br />\n<strong>導演</strong> Fatball（李紹波）、25（楊承恩）<br />\n<strong>主演</strong> 林保怡、周家怡、衛詩雅、陳奐仁、伍詠薇、秦 沛、潘燦良、岑珈其、楊偲泳、陳健朗、談善言、黃定謙、黃溢濠、唐 寧、艾 威、凌文龍、陸駿光、劉兆銘、梁諾妍、易健兒、劉皓嵐<br />\n<strong>集數</strong> 15集<br />\n<br />\n<strong>官方預告</strong><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/FobCZSBZWp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFobCZSBZWp8&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=bc41f7ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FobCZSBZWp8</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n如果睇唔明:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"53ec6c4991bd8e516663373d6fe8fb7d144c9f44","tid":2036624,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"下集好睇<img src=\"/assets/face